summary: Adds an underground warehouse NW of Whiterun
descriptionHtml:
Adds an underground warehouse NW of Whiterun.  Find the \'Wrecked Shack\' to access.  More content will be added as time permits.  I like to display my armor and weapons and there wasn\'t a mod to accommodate my needs.  This will be my first public mod so enjoy.

Adds 36 Weapon Plaques
Adds 36 Weapon/Armor Plaques
Adds 10 Weapon Display Cases
Adds 6 Weapon Racks
Adds 64 mannequins
New fast travel location \'Wrecked Shack\'
New Interior Cell \'Abandoned Warehouse\'

[b][color=red]IMPORTANT: When upgrading from 0.5.1 to 0.5.2 be sure to save outside of Abandoned Warehouse or the plugin will not update properly!![/b]  I have tested the update and found that items on mannequins were unaffected but due to Skyrim glitches anything not affixed to a mannequin *may* be lost.  I recommend a backup save to revert to 0.5.1 just in case.[/color]

No known compatibility issues.  May conflict with mods that add objects to the world where I did.  Otherwise all separate unique cells.  I\'m sorry for the all the Iron shields and greatswords but it is the only way to get the shield/weapon plaque to display properly in game.  Both the shield and swords are replaceable.

Version 0.5.2 (expected release date 6-25-12)
Adds 36 Weapon Plaques
Adds 36 Weapon/Armor Plaques
Adds 10 Weapon Display Cases
Adds 6 Weapon Racks

Version 0.5.1
Enabled World Space entrance

Version 0.5.0
Adds \'Wrecked Shack\' Location to World Space
Adds \'Abandoned Warehouse\' cell
Adds 64 Mannequins
